<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FureverHome</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css">
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'main', media: 'all', 'data-turbo-track': 'reload' %>
</head>
<body>

<section class="hero-section">
    <h1>Your next best friend awaits!</h1>
    <p>Each of our pets is looking for a loving home, and we can't wait to help you find your perfect match.</p>
    <a href="<%= pets_path %>" class="stylish-button">Give a friend a Furever Home</a>
</section>

<section class="stylish-section" id="about-us">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-md-6 text-left">
                <h2>About Our Pets</h2>
                <p>
                    At FureverHome, every pet has a heart full of love just waiting to be shared!
                    From curious kittens to loyal dogs, each of our furry friends has their own unique
                    personality and adorable quirks. We’re here to help you find your perfect companion.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img src="https://images.wagwalkingweb.com/media/daily_wag/blog_articles/hero/1651153661.2751184/a-day-in-the-life-of-an-animal-shelter-volunteer.png" alt="Our Pets" class="img-fluid">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="stylish-section" id="why-adopt">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <img src="https://prodogsdirect.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Happy-puppy-homepage-700x467.jpg" alt="Why Adopt" class="img-fluid">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 text-left mt-4">
                <h2>Why Adopt?</h2>
                <p>
                    Adopting a pet isn’t just about giving them a new home; it’s about giving them a second chance at a happy, fulfilling life.
                    When you adopt, you’re saving a life and opening your heart to an endless source of love and joy. From reducing the number of
                    homeless animals to gaining a loyal companion, the impact of adoption is truly life-changing for both you and your new furry friend.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

</body>
</html>
